{"TopicId":103646,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"KAX Helicopter Rotor Hover Mode?","CreatedByName":"SlabGizor117","CreatedById":135987,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-07T21:50:58Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SlabGizor117","CreatedById":135987,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-07T21:50:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFirst of all, sorry for the Jaden Smith title, I wasn\u0027t sure what to capitalize and what not to. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo, how does hover mode work on the helicopter rotor? I didn\u0027t get to binding it to action groups but I did it in the right click menu and it didn\u0027t do anything. In the video that the KAX Dev made about it, he used action groups to treat his hover mode as the collective and the throttle as main engine throttle. Now I\u0027ll admit I don\u0027t know helicopters well, but I do know that he throttled up and lifted high off the ground then turned on hover mode and it leveled off and gave control of the altitude, but mine doesn\u0027t, it\u0027s still completely controlled by throttle. D:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll try action groups and let you know how it goes.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThanks for your help!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E-Slab\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEDIT: Ok, I added action groups for toggle hover, and decrease/increase hover altitude and it had no effect at all. I looked at the Right-click menu and the buttons are changing the hover height number, but it\u0027s not having any effect. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-07T21:55:37Z\u0022 title=\u002204/07/2015 09:55  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 7, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by SlabGizor117\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pecan","CreatedById":96332,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-08T16:20:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf you are looking for help with a particular mod the best place to ask is in that mod\u0027s thread.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/76668-0-90-Kerbal-Aircraft-Expansion-%28KAX%29-v2-3-4\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKAX is here\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SlabGizor117","CreatedById":135987,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-08T19:36:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThank you, I already did, I figured I\u0027d try other places as well.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jesusthebird","CreatedById":176735,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-15T04:52:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBump. Cannot find an answer. Thread link broken.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-15T05:11:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223021729\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022103646\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492231969\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022176735\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jesusthebird\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, Jesusthebird said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv cl